Colleen Zenk https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Colleen_Zenk 0 Colleen Zenk (born January 20, 1953) is an American actress best known for her role as Barbara Ryan in the daytime TV drama As the World Turns, a role she played from September 1978 until the show left the air in September 2010.
